<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Gallery | JRHomeandProperty</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, navy, #1c1c1c);
      color: silver;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      background: #001f3f;
      padding: 25px;
      border-bottom: 4px solid silver;
    }

    h1 {
      color: silver;
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .back-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: silver;
      color: navy;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .intro {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 25px 20px 5px;
      color: white;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .gallery-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 3px solid silver;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .gallery-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 260px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 2px solid silver;
    }

    .gallery-card h2 {
      color: white;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .gallery-card p {
      color: silver;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>JRHomeandProperty Gallery</h1>
    <a href="index.html" class="back-btn">Back Home</a>
  </header>

  <p class="intro">
    View examples of JRHomeandProperty yard care, cleanup, lawn work,
    and property service photos.
  </p>

  <section class="gallery-grid">

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard1.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 1">
      <h2>Yard 1</h2>
      <p>Yard cleanup and outdoor property service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard2.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 2">
      <h2>Yard 2</h2>
      <p>Grass care, trimming, and property cleanup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard3.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 3">
      <h2>Yard 3</h2>
      <p>Outdoor cleanup and yard improvement work.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard4.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 4">
      <h2>Yard 4</h2>
      <p>Property care and outdoor maintenance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard5.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 5">
      <h2>Yard 5</h2>
      <p>Clean yard space and maintained property area.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard6.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 6">
      <h2>Yard 6</h2>
      <p>Yard work, cleanup, and property service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-card">
      <img src="yard7.jpg" alt="Yard service photo 7">
      <h2>Yard 7</h2>
      <p>Finished yard cleanup and outdoor improvement.</p>
    </div>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
